Thoughts that go in a Pediatrician’s mind when it’s time for your own child’s vaccination. Ofcourse you have some amazing Pediatrician Colleagues who will happily do it for your kid, but you still want to do it yourself.
A part of you wants to postpone the vaccination by few days but another part of you wants to do it ASAP because vaccinations are so important. 

#cuddles_child_care #pediatricianinludhiana #doctormom

A day before this years Doctor’s Day , I thought of sharing my journey of becoming a Pediatrician with my Instagram family. 
Growing up as for many good students in India I also used to tell my parents ( non doctors) that I wanted to become a doctor when I am big. I have no idea how that idea was planted in my mind originally because honestly I wasn’t inspired to see anyone till then. May be it was something I thought would make my parents happy. 
 Eventually I did go on that path, worked super hard and actually started enjoying the journey. When you start getting results in something you are putting efforts in , you want to do more of it. 
Studying was always that for me , effortless and something I knew I was naturally good at.
Was fortunate to clear my exams in first go always and going deeper and deeper into medicine I did realise somewhere at a point that I cannot imagine myself doing anything other than this. 👩‍⚕️ 

P.S- The above journey is just the academic part of those 10 years. Like other adults I too had my share of personal struggles and battles which have transformed me into the person I am proud of today. 

P.S.P.S- Just a girl with a will to not just survive but to thrive!🌸

Happy DOCTORS 🥼 DAY everyone!

I am Dr.Raina Brar, Pediatrician based in Sarabha Nagar, Ludhiana.
I have done my MBBS and MD ( Pediatrics ) from DMCH, Ludhiana and have been running my own clinic in Sarabha Nagar, Ludhiana since 2022. 
I have been engaging actively on Instagram with new mothers all over the world on my profile @cuddles_by_dr.rainabrar from last 2 years. From quite sometime now i have been wanting to start a new Instagram channel in Punjabi where I can interact with my Punjabi moms all over the world in our Ma-Boli.
So here we go.
